name: Daughter's Creations 0001
description:
Modern Urban Experience

It succinctly captures the disparate classes and political leanings in American culture by showing the distinct colors vividly at the edges while expertly blending them in the central confluence. The colors blend a bit there and become harder to discern, but with a close eye you can still see them. Quite apropos of the modern urban experience. Bravo. 10/10 would put crayon in nose.
